---

<BaseLayout
  title="3 Languages = 3x More Buyers | Trilingual SEO Malaysia"
  description="English + Malay + Chinese. One website. Three times more buyers. RM 1,200/month. See how Terasek won RM 60,000 government job with Malay SEO."
  locale={lang}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="text-accent-500 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">Trilingual SEO</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 text-white">
          3 Languages = 3x More Buyers
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          English buyers find you. Malay buyers find you. Chinese buyers find you.
          <br><br>
          <strong>Your competitors use only English. You win.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://wa.me/60175032281?text=Hi%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20Trilingual%20SEO." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
            Start RM399 Trial
          </a>
          <a href="/en/case-studies" class="btn btn-secondary">
            See Real Results
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem: One Language is Not Enough -->
  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card p-8 md:p-12 border-accent-500/50">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 text-center text-white">
            One Language = Missed Sales
          </h2>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-invert">
            <p class="text-secondary-300 text-lg">
              <strong>Most websites:</strong> English only.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-300 text-lg">
              <strong>Problem:</strong> In Malaysia, people speak 3 languages.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-300 text-lg">
              <strong>What happens:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="text-secondary-300 text-lg space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Malay buyers cannot find you (they search in Malay)</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Chinese buyers skip your site (they prefer Chinese)</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Government jobs use Malay (you cannot apply)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-accent-400 text-xl font-bold mt-6">
              You lose 2 out of 3 buyer groups.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Real Proof: Terasek Story -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary-900">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-white">
          Real Proof: RM 60,000 Job Win
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary-400">
          One Malay keyword. One government job. Big result.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card p-8 border-green-500/50">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="text-6xl mb-4">üíßüöõ</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2">{realExample.problem}</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-dark p-6 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-secondary-400 mb-2">English Keyword</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white">"{realExample.english}"</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-secondary-500 mt-2">What expats & corporates search</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-accent-500/20 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-accent-500">
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-accent-400 mb-2">Malay Keyword</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-accent-400">"{realExample.malay}"</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-secondary-300 mt-2">What local buyers & government search</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-secondary-400 mb-2">What Happened</div>
            <p class="text-lg text-secondary-300">{realExample.story}</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-500">
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">The Result</div>
